.START 

Sony USA Inc., a subsidiary of Sony Corp., said about 96.2% of the common stock of Materials Research Corp. was tendered under its $14-a-share offer. 

The cash offer was made through Sony USA's Sony MRC Acquisition Corp. unit. 

Sony USA said it expects Sony MRC and Materials Research to merge around the end of October in accordance with the terms and conditions of the merger agreement.
In the merger, all remaining shares outstanding of Materials Research will be converted into cash at $14 a share, Sony USA said. 

